{"lemma":"عُقُوقٌ","slug":"عُقُوقٌ","root":"ع.ق.ق","root_slug":"ع-ق-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/ع-ق-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n29815"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B9%D9%8F%D9%82%D9%8F%D9%88%D9%82%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n29815","headword_ar":"عَقُوقٌ","root":"Eq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", applied to a mare, (S, O, K, TA,) and to an ass, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Pregnant:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not pregnant after having been covered by the stallion,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"during a year"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"two years"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"some years;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K;) or it signifies thus also; (O;) having two contr. meanings; (K;) or it is applied to one in the latter state as implying a presage of good; (O, K;) so says AHát; (O, TA;) i. e., as though they meant that she would become pregnant: (TA:) it is extr.; [as being from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEaq~ato","text_ar":"اَعَقَّتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":";] and one should not say ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muEiq~N","text_ar":"مُعِقٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; or this is a bad dial. var.; (S, O, K;) or, accord. to AA, it is from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AEq~t","text_ar":"اعقّت"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaquwqN","text_ar":"عَقُوقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eaq~ato","text_ar":"عَقَّتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuquqN","text_ar":"عُقُقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiqaAqN","text_ar":"عِقَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a pl. pl., (S, O, K,) i. e. pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EuquqN","text_ar":"عُقُقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, O.) It is said in a prov.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Talaba AlA^abolaqa","text_ar":"طَلَبَ الاَبْلَقَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEaquwqa","text_ar":"العَقُوقَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He sought an impossible thing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"because"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ablq","text_ar":"ابلق"},{"kind":"text","text":"is applied to a male, and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eqwq","text_ar":"عقوق"},{"kind":"text","text":"means pregnant: (S, O, and K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"blq","text_ar":"بلق"},{"kind":"text","text":") or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlAblq AlEqwq","text_ar":"الابلق العقوق"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the dawn,"},{"kind":"text","text":"because it breaks, lit, cleaves. (O, and K in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"blq","text_ar":"بلق"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nawaY","text_ar":"نَوَى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlEaquwqi","text_ar":"العَقُوقِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Date-stones that are easily broken,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, S, O, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"soft to be chewed;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, O, K;) which are given as provender to camels, (S,) or to the pregnant thereof, in consideration of her state, wherefore they are thus called; and which are eaten, or chewed, by the old woman; but this is of the speech of the people of El Basrah, and not known by the Arabs in their desert: (Lth, O:) and sometimes they called"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a single date-stone of this sort"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaqiyqapN","text_ar":"عَقِيقَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EaAq~N","text_ar":"عَاقٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","O","K","TA","Lth"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}